title: Week Seven Game Talk
text:
Christian James ColoradoPrepReport.com Publisher 
Game Talk is a feature from Colorado Prep Report where we quote some of the top athletes throughout the state on their opponent this week on the football field. Quotes included are from Cherokee Trail vs. Valor Christian, Wiggins vs. Burlington, Liberty vs. Pine Creek, Legend vs. Castle View, and Gateway vs. Heritage. Wiggins athlete Kaeson Risner Opponent - Burlington Football"I think it is going good. It took us a while to find our rhythm but we are doing really well."Vs. Burlington
